  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a libadwaita</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libadwaita</application> package provides additional GTK4
UI widgets for use in developing user interfaces. It is used primarily for
GNOME applications.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

